parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the CVT transmission can cause the vehicle to lose motive power, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: The transmission suddenly stops working
the vehicle loses acceleration
the transmission slips
the vehicle vibrates or shakes
the transmission fluid leaks
the fill cap or vent plug comes loose
and the vehicle is unable to shift into gear.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Transmission Fill Cap or Vent Plug Failure
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the transmission fill cap or vent plug can cause the transmission fluid to leak, leading to transmission failure and loss of motive power.
symptoms: The transmission fill cap or vent plug comes loose
transmission fluid leaks
and the vehicle experiences loss of acceleration or vibration.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the VSA modulator can cause the vehicle to lose traction and stability, leading to accidents.
symptoms: The VSA modulator fails
causing the vehicle to lose traction and stability.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the clutch or axle can cause the vehicle to lose motive power, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: The clutch or axle fails
causing the vehicle to lose acceleration or vibration.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the airbag system can cause the airbags to not deploy in the event of a crash, which can lead to serious injury or death.
symptoms: The airbag warning light is illuminated on the instrument panel
the airbag warning light is flashing on and off
the airbag system warning message appears on the screen
the airbag system is malfunctioning
the airbag inflator is defective
the driver's side airbag is not deploying.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the driver's side airbag inflator can cause the airbag to not deploy in the event of a crash, which can lead to serious injury or death.
symptoms: The airbag warning light is illuminated on the instrument panel
the airbag warning light is flashing on and off
the airbag system warning message appears on the screen
the driver's side airbag inflator is defective
the airbag system is malfunctioning.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the airbag system cable relay can cause the airbag system to malfunction, which can lead to the airbags not deploying in the event of a crash.
symptoms: The airbag warning light is illuminated on the instrument panel
the airbag warning light is flashing on and off
the airbag system warning message appears on the screen
the airbag system cable relay is defective.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the ignition system can cause the vehicle to stall or not start, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: The push start button clicks but doesn't turn the engine on
the key fails to turn over and start the vehicle
the steering wheel is locked
and the vehicle fails to start.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the electrical system can cause the battery to drain, leading to the vehicle stalling or not starting, and potentially resulting in accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: The battery discharges slowly
the vehicle develops an electrical drain
and the tire pressure monitoring system (TPMS) warning light illuminates.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the TPMS can cause the driver to be unaware of low tire pressure, leading to accidents or tire blowouts.
symptoms: The TPMS warning light illuminates
and the system incorrectly indicates low tire pressure.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the accessory power outlet can cause a fire hazard, leading to accidents or injuries.
symptoms: The power outlet fails without tripping the fuse
and the outlet overheats
causing a fire.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the lane watch camera can cause the driver to be unaware of their surroundings, leading to accidents.
symptoms: The lane watch camera fails to function
and the system incorrectly indicates a fault.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the brake system can cause the vehicle to lose braking ability, leading to accidents.
symptoms: The brake light is broken
and the vehicle cannot shift out of park without using a golf tee to override it.
